* 'platescale' for conversion mm -> arcsec
* offset.R1,R2,T1,T2 to take values in mm (convert via platescale)
* pixelsize in mm (converted via platescale)
* Option to restrict analysis to subarrays. e.g. subarray={R,T,R1,R2,T1,T2}
  This is useful to determine subarray offsets / rotations...
* getLocalFixedIndices() with polarray misalignent (offset and rotation)
* log quantities and (also in READMEs).

